<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Guiding Guru</title>
    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%; /* Ensure html and body take full height */
            margin: 0; /* Remove default margin */
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #d4fcdc, #4ba77e);
            color: #333;
        }

        .navbar {
            background-color: #333;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .navbar p {
            color: white;
            float: left;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }

        .navbar a {
            float: right;
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline from links */
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
            color: black;
        }

        .motto {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center; /* Center text inside motto */
            padding: 40px 20px; /* Added padding for spacing */
        }

        .text h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Reduced bottom margin for better spacing */
        }

        .text p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Reduced space below paragraph */
        }

        .search-container {
            display: inline-flex; /* Align search input and button horizontally */
        }

        .search-bar {
            padding: 10px; /* Add padding for better appearance */
            border-radius: 5px; 
            border: 1px solid #ccc; 
            margin-right: 10px; /* Space between input and button */
        }

        .text button {
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            height: 40px;
            padding: 0 20px; 
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px; 
            border: none; /* Remove border */
        }

        .text button:hover {
            background-color: #4ba77e;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            height: calc(100% - 60px); /* Adjust height to fill remaining space below navbar */
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: -50px; /* Adjusted to move it up above the cards */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Reduced bottom margin for better spacing */
        }

        .cards {
           display: flex;
           justify-content: space-around;
           flex-wrap: wrap; 
           width: calc(100% - 40px); /* Full width minus margins */
           padding-bottom: 20px; /* Padding at the bottom of cards section */
           margin-top: 10px; /* Space between motto and cards section */
        }

        .card {
           background-color: white;
           border-radius: 8px; 
           padding: 20px;
           width: calc(30% - 40px); /* Adjusted width for better spacing on larger screens */
           margin-bottom: 20px; 
           transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; 
           box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); /* Added shadow for depth */
           text-align:center; /* Center text inside card */
        }

        .card h3 {
           margin-top: 0; /* Remove top margin for card titles */
           font-size: 20px; /* Adjusted size for card titles */
        }

        .footer {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0; 
        }

        hr {
            border-top: 1px solid #06402B; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="navbar">
        <p>Guiding Guru</p>
        <a href="/about">About Us</a>
        <a href="/login" class="login-link">Login</a>
        <a href="/help">Help</a>
    </div>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="motto">
        <div class="text">
            <h1>Find Your Guru, Fuel Your Future</h1>
            <p>Empowering growth through personalized mentor-mentee connections, fostering meaningful guidance for career success.</p>
            
            <div class="search-container">
                <input type="text" id="mentorSearch" class="search-bar" placeholder="Search for mentors...">
                <button class="search-button" onclick="searchMentors()">Search</button>
                <script>
                    function searchMentors() {
                        const query = document.getElementById('mentorSearch').value.trim();
                        if (query) {
                            window.location.href = `/search?query=${encodeURIComponent(query)}`;
                        }
                    }
                </script>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Moved the section title above the cards -->
        <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Us?</h2> 
        
        <div class="cards">
             <!-- Card content remains unchanged -->
             <div class="card">
                <h3>Find Your Perfect Mentor</h3>
                <p>Explore mentors from various professional domains, carefully matched to your specific career aspirations and goals.</p>
             </div>

             <div class="card">
                <h3>Integrated Chat System</h3>
                <p>Facilitates seamless and secure communication between mentors and mentees.</p>
             </div>

             <div class="card">
                <h3>Join a Thriving Community</h3>
                <p>Connect with peers and mentors who can guide you on your career path.</p>
             </div>
         </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer">
         &copy Guiding Guru. All rights reserved.
    </div>

</body>
</html>
